subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The Longhorns’ D. J. Augustin, A. J. Abrams and Damion James outshined the Cardinal’s 7-footers, combining for 53 points Friday night in second-seeded Texas’s 82-62 victory.
